data.description: Spacious 3-bed, 2-bath doublewide on 2.5 acres in desirable Charlotte County. Open concept floor plan with a well-appointed kitchen and abundant natural light. Cozy bedrooms, master with ensuite. Expansive lot for endless possibilities. Peaceful rural setting close to amenities. Don't miss out on this charming home with heat pump, appliances included, and your own slice of paradise. Schedule a showing today! All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
